June 29, 2026

U.S. Food and Drug Administration
Subject: Voluntary Recall Notification =E2=80=93 Romaine Lettuce Hearts
3-pack, Traceability Lot LOT-2026-0437

To Whom It May Concern:

This letter serves as notice of a voluntary recall concerning Fresh
romaine hearts, 3-count sleeve, ready-to-eat, marketed as Romaine
Lettuce Hearts 3-pack (Product ID PRD-1001), traceability lot code
LOT-2026-0437, produced on 2026-06-01 with expiry date 2026-06-12.

Based on the available source data, the recalling firm is GreenLeaf
Farms Food Safety Team / GreenLeaf Farms. The origin facility
identified in the trace is Salinas Valley Farm, Salinas, California
(Facility ID F-100). FDA registration number: INCOMPLETE.

Reason for recall: Source records indicate a positive laboratory
finding for E. coli O157:H7. The available testing record references
COA-2026-0437 and reports =E2=80=9CDetected in 25g=E2=80=9D on test date 20=
26-06-08
against a specification of =E2=80=9CNot detected / 25g.=E2=80=9D The email =
notice also
states that GreenLeaf QA Laboratory confirmed a positive result for
sample SMP-7001 drawn on 2026-06-07 and tested on 2026-06-08.

Scope of affected product: Total affected quantity is 18,700 EA.
Distributed product was shipped from Salinas Pack House to the
following downstream distribution points: FreshPack Distribution
(4,200 EA; BOL-50021), WestCoast Grocery DC (8,800 EA; BOL-50022),
Southwest Foods DC (3,100 EA; BOL-50023), and Rocky Mountain Foods DC
(2,600 EA; BOL-50024). States identified as affected in the source
trace are AZ, CA, CO, and TX.

Actions taken to date: Source records indicate immediate recall
urgency, downstream notification initiation request, and quarantine
holds on identified warehouse inventory. Warehouse inventory listed on
hold totals 2,850 EA across inventory records INV-0001, INV-0002, and
INV-0003. Trace records show complete critical tracking event coverage
for the available lot trace data.

Point of contact: Maria Lopez, QA Manager, AgriSeed Co,
qa@agriseed.com, +1-831-555-0142. Recalling firm contact details
beyond the provided records are INCOMPLETE.

Please note that this notice is based solely on the source data
provided for compliance package preparation. Certain mandatory
elements remain incomplete where unsupported by the record.

Sincerely,

